{"article_id":"BiCI6i8AffCUt59W","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un ' s surprise announcement","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that his nation will suspend tests of nuclear weapons and missiles","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and close its nuclear testing site","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"sounds like a momentous victory for the U.S.","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"It ' s not -","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"at least , not yet .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Kim ' s announcement Saturday","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"( local time )","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"may simply be a ploy","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"to ensure","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"President Trump meets with Kim in the coming weeks ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"conferring international prestige on the dictator","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"and paving the way for the lifting of international economic sanctions","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"crippling his impoverished nation .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Before we start singing \" Give Peace a Chance \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and celebrating a victory by the Trump administration","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"for forcing Kim to back down ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"let ' s pause .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Remember","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that Kim simply made a statement","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"- and he has a long record","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"of lying and breaking promises on the nuclear issue and other issues .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"While Kim ' s conciliatory words are certainly welcome ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"there ' s no way","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"of knowing","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"whether he will actually do what he claims .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Before we start singing \" Give Peace a Chance \"","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and celebrating a victory by the Trump administration","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"for forcing Kim to back down ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"let ' s pause .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Remember","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that Kim simply made a statement","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"- and he has a long record","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"of lying and breaking promises on the nuclear issue and other issues .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"At this point , Kim has given away absolutely nothing .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"All","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he has to do","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"is give an order","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and North Korea can resume testing nuclear weapons and missiles again .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"And of critical importance ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Kim gave no indication","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"he plans to destroy his small but devastating nuclear arsenal and missiles","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that he has already developed -","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"or his large conventional armed forces and armaments .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"He already has the ability","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to kill millions of people with the nuclear weapons and missiles","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that he has on hand ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"without developing any new ones .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Kim may simply be trying to show signs","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that he is willing to make major concessions","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"to have better relations with the United States , South Korea and Japan , along with the international community .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"He has plenty of reasons to be on his best behavior over the next few weeks ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"showing","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that he can be reasonable , rational and open to a long-term détente .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The North Korean leader will meet on Friday in the week ahead with South Korean President Moon Jae-in .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"And plans are underway for the first-ever meeting between U.S. and North Korean leaders in coming weeks .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Remember the cold hard reality of what we witnessed back in 2017 .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"Kim might not need to conduct many more missile or nuclear tests","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"to know","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he can hit targets in the U.S. homeland .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Kim tested three intercontinental ballistic missiles","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"( ICBMs )","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"- part of a sprint of over 20 missile tests last year -","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that showed","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"North Korea had the range and technological prowess","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to strike as far as New York City and even Washington , D.C .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"In September , Kim also tested a hydrogen bomb","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"- the most destructive of all nuclear weapons .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"One of these bombs could wipe any U.S. city off the map , with horrific casualties .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"So Kim is now very close to having a fully capable , albeit tiny , nuclear force with global reach .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"All","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that is needed","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"is the ability","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"for his warheads to re-enter the Earth ' s atmosphere","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"and land on target .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"And we know ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"at least according to one report ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that Kim has at least a crude capability","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to see his warheads survive the massive heat and wind shears","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to rain down atomic terror on his enemies .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Since Kim last tested an ICBM","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"- or any missile -","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"in November ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he has had months of lab research time","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"to perfect even more of his nuclear weapons arsenal and missiles .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Kim may have gambled","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that announcing a closure of his atomic testing grounds and suspending missile and nuclear weapons tests will gain him tremendous international goodwill , a meeting with the U.S. president","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"- and result in him losing nothing .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Kim could easily start to test missiles at any time","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"he wishes .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"And he doesn ' t need missiles","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"flying all throughout Northeast Asia","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"to perfect the targeting , guidance , command and control and heatshield technology of his nuclear delivery systems in small ways .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Perfecting all these things could have very big results months or years down the line","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"if Kim decides to change his mind","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"and begin missile testing again .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"The same goes for nuclear weapons .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Just because Kim closes his nuclear testing area","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"doesn ' t mean he can ' t open it back up again .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"The testing site","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"- a series of carefully crafted deep underground tunnels","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that took time","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"to construct -","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"is not a sophisticated lab .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"So let ' s not get carried away","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"and be so impressed .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Again ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"as I noted just recently in a Fox News Opinion piece ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"what Kim is likely doing is setting the craftiest of traps -","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"one","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"designed to suck the Trump administration into months or years of negotiations .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"All the while , Kim ' s scientists are working","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"to perfect his deadly arsenal of weapons of mass destruction","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"- not just nuclear weapons , but also chemical and likely biological weapons as well .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"The Trump administration must move past Kim ' s dramatic announcement","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"that was designed to pull at our emotions","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"and make us hopeful","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"that peace is at hand .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"We must demand deeds ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"because as the old saying goes ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"actions speak louder than words .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Particularly in Kim ' s case .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"For example , the Trump administration should insist on a roadmap","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"whereby Kim lays out how he will get rid of his nuclear weapons for good","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"- before any U.S.-North Korea summit .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Any agreement with the North should be contingent on international inspectors having 24-hour access to all parts of North Korea","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"- with no site off limits and no notification of access .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"If inspectors are not allowed to go anywhere , anytime in North Korea","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"without notice","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"there is no real basis for a deal .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"Also , any lifting of the international maximum pressure campaign on North Korea must be contingent on Kim making measured and definable progress on giving up his nukes .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"He must give verifiable proof","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"that he is getting rid of his atomic arsenal","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"to see economic sanctions lifted .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"While I am hopeful","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"that Kim could really be sincere in giving up his nukes ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"public declarations and easily reversed measures are meaningless .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"I can only hope","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"the Trump administration sees it the same way .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":277,"left":152,"right":276,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":144,"right":151,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":142,"right":143,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":0,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":148,"right":150,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":146,"right":147,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":11,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":193,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":163,"right":192,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":159,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":155,"right":158,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":154,"right":17,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":14,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":18,"right":157,"relation":"attribution